    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>通过正确完成任务来管理你的地下快餐业务：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281090/extras/47db175b185ae01682d61b62fd524940.avif?t=1767645147\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281090/extras/2c8a37337b8914ca63263a268f97a5db.poster.avif?t=1767645147\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281090/extras/2c8a37337b8914ca63263a268f97a5db.webm?t=1767645147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281090/extras/2c8a37337b8914ca63263a268f97a5db.mp4?t=1767645147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >记录各种怪物的独特需求，满足他们的不同口味。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281090/extras/a9cef6274044441103d441b94812d5bc.avif?t=1767645147\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281090/extras/e94ec24c43da943cdafc865eee997655.poster.avif?t=1767645147\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281090/extras/e94ec24c43da943cdafc865eee997655.webm?t=1767645147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281090/extras/e94ec24c43da943cdafc865eee997655.mp4?t=1767645147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将人类研磨成优质肉品。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281090/extras/305c1936725b657de555a7e1cde34d6c.avif?t=1767645147\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281090/extras/9a499546bbdca98681cd1d7027bc1aeb.poster.avif?t=1767645147\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281090/extras/9a499546bbdca98681cd1d7027bc1aeb.webm?t=1767645147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281090/extras/9a499546bbdca98681cd1d7027bc1aeb.mp4?t=1767645147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将肉类制作成各种美食。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281090/extras/b9275bea00332d3cf7cecadf587e4645.avif?t=1767645147\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281090/extras/9e4baeaffeb7425c39f48418be7c2386.poster.avif?t=1767645147\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281090/extras/9e4baeaffeb7425c39f48418be7c2386.webm?t=1767645147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281090/extras/9e4baeaffeb7425c39f48418be7c2386.mp4?t=1767645147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精心准备食物，记得不要烧焦哦！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281090/extras/1057a020248824abbe5ed6772085b595.avif?t=1767645147\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281090/extras/00366071313010180e0dbaeda570ff55.poster.avif?t=1767645147\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281090/extras/00366071313010180e0dbaeda570ff55.webm?t=1767645147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281090/extras/00366071313010180e0dbaeda570ff55.mp4?t=1767645147\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为顾客提供美食，赚取你的利润。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>额外功能：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受轻松的黑暗幻想风格。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >管理库存，购买新食材。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自定义你的餐厅，打造独一无二的风格。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级厨房设备，让它们更快、更美观、更高效。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雇佣怪物助手，帮助你</p></li></ul>",
